OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMartyn's Law for venue     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fsecurity to cover all of UK
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, New legislation will be introduced to  
OL,6, tighten security at venues in the wake 
OL,7, of the Manchester Arena bombing.       
OL,9,FThe new rules, dubbed Martyn's Law,    
OL,10,Fwill cover all of the UK and require   
OL,11,Fvenues and local authorities to have   
OL,12,Fpreventative action plans against      
OL,13,Fterror attacks, the government said.   
OL,15,FMartyn Hett was among 22 people killed 
OL,16,Fin the 2017 attack and his mother Figen
OL,17,FMurray has campaigned for the measures.
OL,19,FDraft legislation is due in early      
OL,20,Fspring, the prime minister said.       
